80823144308_93029.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong>The honor and title</strong> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> <span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong>荣誉头衔</strong> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">● 西婵整形美容医院韩籍注册医师、整形外科专业医师</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> <span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">● 首尔白医院临床讲师与专职讲师</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> <span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">● 仁济大学医学院整形外科客座教授</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> <span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">● 整形再造面部畸形研究所研究员</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> <span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> </span> <span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">● 大韩整形颚矫正手术研究会员</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> <span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">● 大韩整形外科联合会正式会员</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> <span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">● 大韩整形外科学会正式会员</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong>Field of expertise</strong> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> <span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong>擅长领域</strong> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<strong> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">· 颜面轮廓塑形 ·</span></strong> \r\n</div>\r\n</strong> <span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">面部五官微创雕塑、颧骨、下颌角整形以及面部轮廓自然塑形等整形外科手术；</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<strong> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">· 脂肪移植整形 ·</span></strong> \r\n</div>\r\n</strong> <span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">溶脂减肥、体型塑造、全身及面部自体脂肪移植填充；</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<strong> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">· 乳房整形 ·</span></strong> \r\n</div>\r\n</strong> <span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">自体脂肪丰胸、假体丰胸等常规、疑难性胸部整形美容手术以及胸部整形手术失败修复；</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<strong> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">· 鼻、眼部整形 ·</span></strong> \r\n</div>\r\n</strong> <span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">各类常规鼻、眼部整形美容手术；</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<strong> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">· 其他整形 ·</span></strong> \r\n</div>\r\n</strong> <span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">面部拉皮除皱、耳垂粘连矫正、耳前方疤痕治疗等整形美容手术；</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong>▏Personal profile</strong> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> <span style=\"font-size:16px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong>个人简介</strong> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> \r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-weight:normal;font-size:9.0000pt;\"><span>来自于韩国，被誉为是韩国改脸型大师，韩星</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-weight:normal;font-size:9.0000pt;\"><span>指定</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-weight:normal;font-size:9.0000pt;\"><span>整形美容顾问的金振玉医生，是西婵特邀韩国籍整形外科专业医师。他从事整形美容行业</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-weight:normal;font-size:9.0000pt;\">20余年，精通韩式艺术整形，拥有丰富的临床经验和精湛的外科手术技术，擅长多类整形外科手术。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-weight:normal;font-size:9.0000pt;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-weight:normal;font-size:9.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>在从医的职业道路中，金振玉医生曾多次与欧美及中国美容专家进行技术交流，在国际专业整形杂志发表论文多篇。他对面部五官微创雕塑、面部轮廓塑形方面具有独到的见解及技术，对体形塑造和溶脂减肥，整形美容手术失败修复具有颇深的研究和造诣。曾打造出多位韩国明星和选美冠军，在韩国以及国际社会上具有较大的影响力。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-weight:normal;font-size:9.0000pt;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-weight:normal;font-size:9.0000pt;\">2015年参与并录制了中国首档大型人气焕美节目《SHESAYS西婵美人制造》，为多位参与焕美录制的求美者打造出了理想的身形、脸型以及自然无瑕的面容，配以谦和有礼的诊疗态度，深受广大求美者们的喜爱以及业内医师们的尊敬。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-weight:normal;font-size:9.0000pt;\"></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"></span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong>▏Examples show</strong> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> <span style=\"font-size:16px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong>实例展示</strong> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\"><strong>“揭秘颜面轮廓焕美蜕变”</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><strong>匠心独运，不差毫厘，金振玉致力于打造无瑕轮廓曲线</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">面部综合塑形</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161111/20161111165733_82570.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161111/20161111165749_87302.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161111/20161111165802_33969.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161111/20161111165819_57724.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161111/20161111165835_15320.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161111/20161111165851_67897.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">侧颜综合塑形</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161111/20161111165930_34417.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n</span> \r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\">（before/after）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161111/20161111165948_48941.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">（before/after）</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161111/20161111170002_10477.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:21px;\">（before/after）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">颧骨整形</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161111/20161111170029_70043.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">（before/after）</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">下颌角整形</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161111/20161111170052_99848.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">（before/after）</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">颧骨、下颌角整形</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161111/20161111170107_41802.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">（before/after）</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">下巴整形</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161111/20161111170123_83204.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">（before/after）</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">下颌角、下巴整形</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161111/20161111170136_97099.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">（before/after）</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161111/20161111170151_63250.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">（before/after）</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 在对求美者进行面部轮廓塑形的过程中，金振玉医生始终坚持着匠心独运、精益求精的焕美理念，凭借扎实的整形外科医学知识理论功底以及精湛娴熟的外科手术操作经验，致力为求美者打造出符合自身整体气质、不差毫厘的自然面部轮廓，尽情绽放自信光彩，遇见助力美的自己！</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\"><strong>“揭秘脂肪移植自然塑形”</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><strong>变“肥”为宝，轻松塑形，极力打造自然动人曲线</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\">手臂吸脂塑形</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161108/20161108173126_41821.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">（before/after）</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">腿部吸脂塑形</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161111/20161111170206_22823.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">（before/after）</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">臂部吸脂塑形</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161111/20161111170217_67164.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">（before/after）</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 对于脂肪移植整形，金振玉始终秉承在打造自然动人身体曲线的同时，必须要保障求美者们在术前、中、后的焕美轻松，以达到轻松吸脂、塑造体形的目的。焕美过程中会根据求美者们的自身身体情况以及术前检查的相关数据，进行精细的溶脂减肥、体型塑造、全身及面部自体脂肪移植填充，以保障无瑕的焕美效果！</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\"><strong>“揭秘乳房整形华丽蜕变”</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><strong>360°全方位自然塑造，成就焕美经典，绽放自信光彩</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\">常规丰胸</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161111/20161111170229_62292.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 针对不用原因导致的乳房发育不良、发育过盛或是因后天导致的乳房缺失等，金振玉医生均可为不同需求的求美者打造出符合自身气质的自然乳房，360°全方位自然塑造，只为成就焕美经典，让女性无尽绽放自信光彩！</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> <span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 与此同时，金振玉医生还擅长于修复因不同原因导致的失败丰胸术以及操作疑难性胸部整形美容手术。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\"><strong>“揭秘鼻、眼部整形蜕变秘诀”</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><strong>焕美零瑕疵，将天生的“缺点”逆转为你的闪光点</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\">重睑、开眼角</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161111/20161111170244_21653.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">隆鼻及各类鼻部修复</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161111/20161111170257_49355.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 玲珑水亮的大眼和翘挺无瑕的美鼻能够增添整个人的气质与自信，然而，并不是所有的人天生就有自然无瑕的眼睛和鼻子，在不影响美观的情况下，这对整个人的气质与气场并不会带来太大的影响与烦恼。然而，影响到美观的眼、鼻部轮廓及形态则会让整个人的面部、气质与自信度都大打折扣。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> <span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 针对于眼、鼻部有焕美需求的求美者，金振玉会根据求美者的自身状态及气质1对1制定私人焕美方案，运用助力的眼、鼻部整形技术对求美者的眼睛、鼻子部位进行精细改造，将天生的“缺点”逆转为你的闪光点，达到柔美、得体、自然的术后效果，给人以生动、舒适之感，整体提升气质与自信！</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong>▏Learn the infinite</strong> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> <span style=\"font-size:16px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<strong>齐驱并进，媒体跟踪报道</strong> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> <span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">致力于整形美容行业的同时投身公益事业</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161111/20161111170325_65211.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">金振玉医生的行医资格证</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161108/20161108175908_26976.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">韩媒报道整形界翘楚金振玉</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161108/20161108175922_74259.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">金振玉院长参与面部畸形儿童救助行动并被韩媒报道</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161108/20161108175937_30733.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">韩媒报道金振玉院长在整形手术方面的精湛技艺</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161108/20161108180017_46768.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">金振玉院长在第十届韩日整形手术高端峰会上发言</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161111/20161111170423_59658.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> \r\n<div style=\"text-align:center