20161107101845_61514.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;\">汶川地震后，王涛医师随医疗组深入灾区参加医疗救援工作</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;\"><strong>| His work</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;\"><strong>工作中的他</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161107/20161107101918_31167.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;\">工作中的王涛严谨而专注</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;\">将每一个环节做到尽善尽美</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;\"><strong>| His life</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;\"><strong>生活中的他</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161107/20161107102119_37399.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;\">生活中的王涛热爱旅游、阅尽江山美景</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;\">手握手术刀的他依然拥有一个诗意的灵魂</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', '51', '1449049524', '10', '0', '长期坐诊', '西婵泛亚店', '0', '西婵整形外科副主任医师', '0', '1848', '0', '', '王涛：西婵整形外科副主任医师', '');
