1.5;font-size:14px;\">● 四川省医师协会皮肤科医师分会会员</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;\">●&nbsp;艾尔建乔雅登注射临床诊疗医师&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:21px;\">●&nbsp;</span>安束喜临床应用注射诊疗医师&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:21px;\">●&nbsp;</span>得玛莎正品联盟合作机构注射医师&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:21px;\">●&nbsp;</span>人源干细胞培养液AAPE注射医师<br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;\"><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">▏&nbsp;</span></strong></strong>Field of expertise</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;\"><strong>擅长领域</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;\"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;\"><strong>▪ 激光美容 ▪</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;\">祛雀斑、黄褐斑、真皮斑、老年斑、咖啡斑、太田痣等各类色素性损美疾病及激光祛疤、祛痤疮等常规美容项目。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;\"><strong>▪ 抗衰管理 ▪</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;\">超音波拉皮、射频抗衰、热玛吉等抗衰修复护理以及美容嫩肤管理。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;\">▪<strong> 皮肤敏感修复 ▪</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;\">改善因皮肤敏感引起的各类红血丝、面部潮红等肌肤亚健康状态。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;\"><strong>▪ 注射美容 ▪&nbsp;</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">水光针、瘦脸针、注射除皱、祛颈纹、溶脂以及玻尿酸注射塑形、填充等</span>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;\"><strong>▏ Personal profile</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;\"><strong>个人简介</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;\"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;丁艳，西婵乐山分院美容皮肤科主诊医师。毕业于成都中医药大学，从事医学美容工作多年，有丰富的临床经验。从业过程中，曾多次跟随业内医师进修、学习，是医学美容、皮肤美容领域十分具有潜力的年轻医师。</span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;丁医生具有扎实的医学美容理论知识与娴熟的激光、美容等助力仪器设备的操作技艺以及精湛的医学美容注射手法，擅长使用各类激光仪器设备对皮肤进行美容护理。包括嫩肤、紧致抗衰、微创注射，以及对雀斑、黄褐斑、老年斑、真皮斑等皮肤色素性疾病，痤疮、红胎记（鲜红斑痣、毛细血管扩张等），黑胎记（太田痣、咖啡斑等）的治疗。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 凭借谦和温和的处事态度和精湛的医术，丁医生让求美者体验到轻松、舒适、有效的焕美服务，帮助无数爱美女性重获新生！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;\"><strong>▏ Examples show</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;\"><strong>实例展示</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;\"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;\"><strong>面部红血丝+瘦脸+镭射嫩肤美白</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;\"><strong><img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161116/20161116164731_87442.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;丁医生通常会根据求美者皮肤状况，定制一对一的诊疗方案，术前求美者肤质状况较差，红血丝较严重，术后皮肤呈现健康、光滑、紧致的状态。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;\"><strong>▏Experts elegant demeanour</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;\"><strong>医师风采</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:21px;\">严谨务实 &nbsp;追求卓越</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;\"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;\"><strong><img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161116/20161116164757_85544.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\">丁艳医生参加激光美容培训会，不断提升专业技能</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20161116/20161116164922_68150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;\">严谨务实是丁艳医生的工作准则</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p st