><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#999999;font-size:14px;\">将德国进口睫毛生长因子导入睫毛毛囊</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#999999;font-size:14px;\">实现毛囊的二次赋活、新生</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#999999;font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20170414/20170414170139_66002.gif\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#999999;\">它能够</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#999999;\">↓</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#DFC5A4;\"><strong>刺激垂死睫毛毛囊恢复生机</strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#DFC5A4;\"><strong>令静止及衰退中的毛囊重新活跃</strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#DFC5A4;\"><strong>刺激色素细胞产生黑色素</strong></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#999999;\">从而</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#999999;\">保持睫毛乌黑光亮</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#999999;\">实现自身原有睫毛的自然生长</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#999999;\">没有年龄限制，随时想做就做</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#999999;\"><strong>！！！且一次操作，长期见效！！！</strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#999999;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#999999;\"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Uploads/editor/image/20170414/20170414170244_59062.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#999999;\">孕睫术前、后对比效果</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#DFC5A4;\"><strong>SHESAYS 孕睫术